Faits marquants AEE

     * Gap between real-world and type-approval emissions undermines
       incentives for cleaner cars
     * Collecting litter and data to combat plastic pollution
     * EU on track to end use of chemicals harming the ozone layer
     * How to accelerate change towards sustainability?
     * Climate change threatens future of farming in Europe
     * EU Member States make only mixed progress in reducing emissions
       under UN convention, latest air pollution data shows

   Plus

Dernières publications de l'AEE

     * Fiscal instruments favouring electric over conventional cars are
       greener
     * Ozone depleting substances 2019
     * Sustainability transitions: policy and practice
     * Climate change adaptation in the agriculture sector in Europe
     * Knowledge for a sustainable Europe | A snapshot from the European
       Environment Agency
     * European Union emissions inventory report 2017

   Plus

Appels d'offres AEE

     * EEA/DIS/R0/19/012 - Framework service contract for the Copernicus
       Land monitoring services – CLC+ Backbone production, including
       raster and vector products based on Satellite input data from
       2017/2018/2019
     * EEA/ADS/19/005 - Provision of security, reception and mail services
       for the European Environment Agency (EEA)
     * EEA/COM/19/003 - Provision of multimedia and audio-visual services
       for the European Environment Agency (EEA)
     * EEA/COM/19/002 - Support services related to participation to or
       organization of events and exhibitions for the European Environment
       Agency (2 lots)
     * EEA/DIS/R0/19/007 – High Resolution Vegetation Phenology and
       Productivity Monitoring – Biophysical Parameters – Copernicus Land
       Monitoring Service

   Plus

